---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { colors } from "../theme";
export const theme = colors;
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <main>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
    <p>
      Whimsy by Nada ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your
      privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we handle information that you
      provide when using our website, www.whimsybynada.com (the "Website"). By
      using the Website, you agree to this policy.
    </p>

    <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>
      We do not collect or store any personal information on this Website. The
      only information we may receive is your email address and the message you
      provide through the contact form, which is used solely for the purpose of
      corresponding with you regarding commissioned projects.
    </p>

    <h2>3. Use of Information</h2>
    <p>
      The email address you provide via the contact form will only be used to:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Respond to your inquiries</li>
      <li>Correspond regarding your commissioned project</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      We do not use your email for marketing or promotional purposes unless you
      explicitly request it.
    </p>

    <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
    <p>
      We take reasonable precautions to protect the information you provide
      through the contact form. However, as with any online communication, we
      cannot guarantee the absolute security of data.
    </p>

    <h2>5. No Payments or Financial Information</h2>
    <p>
      We do not process payments or collect any financial information through
      the Website. All financial transactions, if any, will be arranged
      separately and outside the Website.
    </p>

    <h2>6. Third-Party Sharing</h2>
    <p>
      We do not share, sell, or disclose any information you provide via the
      contact form with third parties, except as necessary to comply with the
      law or protect our rights.
    </p>

    <h2>7. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
    <p>
      We do not use cookies, tracking technologies, or analytics services to
      collect data about your browsing activity on the Website.
    </p>

    <h2>8. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>
      Since we do not collect personal information beyond the email you
      voluntarily provide through the contact form, there is no personal data
      stored or processed that would require access, correction, or deletion.
    </p>

    <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be
      posted on this page. Your continued use of the Website constitutes your
      acceptance of these changes.
    </p>

    <h2>10. Contact</h2>
    <p>
      If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy,
      please contact us via the contact form on the Website or email
      whimsybynada@gmail.com.
    </p>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  :root {
    --black: ${theme.black};
  }
  main {
    margin: auto;
    padding: 1rem;
    width: 1000px;
    max-width: calc(100% - 2rem);
    color: var(--balck);
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    text-align: center;
    font-family: "Arial, sans-serif";
  }
</style>
